Description:
InDomain detection is a tool designed to extract in-domain data from a large collections of data.
Requirements 
***Python3.6
***KenLM:
	Dowlnload from here: https://kheafield.com/code/kenlm/
***Moses :
	Download from here : https://github.com/moses-smt/mosesdecoder.git
***Python Libraries
	run: pip install -r requirements.txt

Usage:

Folder Structure : 
Work_Path
	|
	|>>>Input_LM
	|
	|>>>Input_test_Indomain
	|
	|>>>lib
	|
	|>>>log
	|
	|>>>Output_LM
	|
	|>>>Output_test_Indomain

InDomain Detection have: 
	3 steps 
	2 mode 
	
Mode 1 : ****Run all****
	By running L0_DD_Full_Runner.py , This will train Language Model then get Indomain Score and finally extract the best InDomain sentences
example :
python3.6 ./lib/L0_DD_Full_Runner.py \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/lib/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_LM/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Output_LM/ \
en \
5 \
/opt/mosesdecoder/ \
/opt/kenlm/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/log/  \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Output_test_Indomain/ \
0

Mode 2 ****Run by step****
###Step One: Tokenize input Data and LM Training
Example: 
python3.6 ./lib/P1_DD_TokandLM.py \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_LM/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Output_LM/ \
en \
5 \
/opt/mosesdecoder/ \
/opt/kenlm/ \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/log

###Step Two:  get Indomain Score
Example:
python3.6 ./lib/P2_DD_LMScoring.py \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.txt \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.scoring.xml \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Output_LM/EN_Lm.bin \
/opt/mosesdecoder/ \
en \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/log/
	
###Step Three : Extract best Indomain sentences
Example:
python3.6 ./lib/P3_DD_Extract.py \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.txt \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.scoring.xml \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.extracted-score.txt \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/Input_test_Indomain/DD_file_test.extracted-sentences.txt \
/opt/Paracrawl_Domain_Detection/DD_work_path/log/